item.description:
This is a Pre-St. Patrick's Day event with lots of Dancing, Great food and the best friends anywhere. Come on down to Sizzle's Bistro, have something to eat and drink, and sing and dance to some great songs with us. Lets see who can do the best "Danny Boy" (or Danielle Girl). All drafts are $3 and the karaoke and dancing are free and fun.
Sizzle Bistro is in the Executive Health Club building by Manchester Airport.
